cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object pose estimation from RGB-D images. It also involves robotics (cs.RO) as the task of grasping and manipulation is mentioned. Machine learning (cs.LG) is also a likely sub-category as the paper mentions the use of attention mechanisms and fusion strategies to learn discriminative multi-modal features. Artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) are also possible sub-categories as the paper deals with the use of multiple modalities to improve object pose estimation.
